{"tid":1990867,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美媒《自由燈塔》：國會研立法禁鳳凰衛視向美國廣播中共政治宣傳","createTime":"2020-04-27T04:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T05:10:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"78bbba6e7e9a83a5486a1ca39f9d2cf2adf25353","tid":1990867,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"華盛頓自由燈塔》（Free Beacon）報道，參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）草擬立法文件以禁止中國共產黨利用美國法律的漏洞，透過一家同鳳凰衛視有關聯的電台，向美國人民發放政治宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n《自由燈塔》指，獲得該立法文件的副本，當中提出如果任何人企圖在收購電台後，改變其廣播語言，則禁止美國聯邦通信委員會（ Federal Communications Commission,簡稱，FCC）發出相關營運牌照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%AA%92-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%87%88%E5%A1%94-%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E7%A0%94%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E9%B3%B3%E5%87%B0%E8%A1%9B%E8%A6%96%E5%90%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%92%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E7%2587%2588%25E5%25A1%2594-%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E5%2587%25B0%25E8%25A1%259B%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%2592%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3%2F&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4EBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=a742b54e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E7%2587%2588%25E5%25A1%2594-%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E5%2587%25B0%25E8%25A1%259B%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%2592%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3%2F&h=03e7f2c9\" target=\